Syria that it is ready to discuss all issues with Damascus,
including Israeli withdrawal of troops to the June 4, 1967 border
as demanded by Syria.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, in an interview with Israeli Hebrew paper Ma'ariv
on Saturday, Chief of Israeli Northern Command Amiram Levine
addressed a prospect of war with Syria, saying that Syrian troops
deployment along the border indicates they are preparing for a
war. 
