<P>
To strengthen Party building ideologically, it is essential to
unswervingly arm the entire Party with Deng Xiaoping Theory and
give full play to the ideological and political strength of the
Party. Deng Xiaoping Theory has provided a new powerful
ideological weapon that will enable our Party to understand the
world and to change it. The entire Party should attach great
importance to study, be adept at studying and usher in a new
upsurge in studying Marxism-Leninism, Mao Zedong Thought and
particularly Deng Xiaoping Theory. Leading cadres at all levels,
and especially the several hundred members of the Party Central
