need to study, to be political-minded and to be honest and
upright. We shall make it a common practice within the entire
Party to study conscientiously, hold democratic discussions, try
to explore new ways and be realistic and pragmatic. We should
continue to integrate theory with practice, study for the sake of
application, acquire a better understanding of the theory of
Marxism, learn to better solve practical problems and transform
our subjective world while transforming the objective world.
</P>
