<HEADLINE> Full Text of Jiang Zemin's Report at 15th Party Congress (45) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
To improve the Party's style of work, it is essential to stick
o the aim of serving the people wholeheartedly and give full play
to the Party's strength in forging close links with the masses.
The fine work styles of integrating theory with practice, forging
close links with the masses and practicing criticism and
self-criticism, which our Party has cultivated in the process of
